Our proposal for smart mirror has been approved. So basically, this mirror will be able to show us the current dtae, time ,weather, and will also include alexa for communication. To enhance the project we are also  planning to add a prototype for a small light to show that our mirror is also able to control and access home automation.Amazon web services provides a facility to build you own way of computing the execution
So combining AWS and automation creates a new instance of technology.
